    "ACTIVITY_FEED": "Match Feed",
    "RESULT_PANEL": "Result",
    "START_ACTION": "PLAY",
    "EXIT_ACTION": "QUIT"
  },
  "_comment_flow": "Everything below drives the default lobby flow (FrameworkFlow). Rename / recolour freely — no code changes needed.",
